snippet.title: Procession escorts casket of fallen L.A. County sheriff's detective  to mortuary I ABC7
snippet.description:
A procession travels through the streets of Los Angeles for sheriff's Detective Amber Leist, who was off-duty when she was fatally struck by a vehicle after helping a couple cross a street in Valley Village over the weekend. Details: https://abc7.la/35RNeJP
